code: /**  * @return true if hostname verification is enabled  */ public abstract boolean isHostnameVerificationEnabled().

comment: /**  * @return true if certificate verification is enabled  */
code: /**  * @return true if certificate verification is enabled  */ public abstract boolean isCertificateVerificationEnabled().

public static VerificationMode parse(String value) {     assert value != null.     switch(value.toLowerCase(Locale.ROOT)) {         case "none":             return NONE.         case "certificate":             return CERTIFICATE.         case "full":             return FULL.         default:             throw new IllegalArgumentException("could not resolve verification mode. unknown value [" + value + "]").     } }
